@startuml

title MCP Tool Execution - Sequence Diagram

autonumber

participant "Agent Runtime" as Runtime
participant "Policy Enforcer" as Policy
participant "MCP Registry" as Registry
participant "MCP Server" as MCP
participant "Corporate System" as System
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Audit Service" as Audit
participant "Billing Service" as Billing

Runtime -> Policy: Validate tool permission
Policy --> Runtime: Allowed
Runtime -> Registry: Discover tool schema and endpoint
Registry --> Runtime: Tool metadata, version and policies
Runtime -> MCP: Execute tool
MCP -> System: Call corporate API
System --> MCP: Business response
MCP --> Runtime: Tool result
Runtime -> Kafka: Publish tool.executed
Kafka -> Audit: Consume tool.executed
Kafka -> Billing: Consume tool usage

@enduml
